ects, designers, engineers, scholars of human evolutionary biology, and-with more than one hundred striking images of designs-anyone interested in nature†'inspired spaces.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 0aArchitecturexEnvironmental aspects. 7aARCHITECTURE / Interior Design / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300235432423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300235432.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles